query:
INSERT INTO
            protocol_versions (
                id,
                bootloader_code_hash,
                default_account_code_hash,
                upgrade_tx_hash,
                recursion_scheduler_level_vk_hash,
                executed,
                created_at
            )
            VALUES
            ($1, $2, $3, $4, $5, FALSE, NOW())
            ON CONFLICT (id) DO
            UPDATE
            SET
            upgrade_tx_hash = excluded.upgrade_tx_hash,
            executed = FALSE;
